### Create new quiz session
POST /api/game-sessions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chainId": 1
}

### Submit correct answer
POST /api/game-sessions/1/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": 1,
  "answer": "H2O"
}

### Submit incorrect answer
POST /api/game-sessions/1/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "questionId": 2,
  "answer": "Wrong Answer"
}

### Check session progress
GET /api/game-sessions/1